result.name: Dragon House

reviews.text: It was our last full day in Hong Kong and I really wanted to try their dim sum.  My friends suggested this place since their family often dined here.  After doing some shopping in Causeway Bay, we used Google maps to find this little gem.  The place looked neat and patrons were chatting with one another while eating. Each of us ordered our favorite dishes.  The meal was excellent and affordable and the wait staff were so helpful...some also spoke to us in English. They even offered free wifi. =)
the best snake cuisine specially prepared by the chef for us.  Hong Kong's best fresh snake soup
The environment is great.  Seating arrangement is very comfortable.
No deco but reasonable price food at reasonable quality.  No need to finish your meal within definite time .  Good choice if u want to gather in causeway bay
Good food in quality and style at a reasonable price

reviews.text: 食品相當出色，尢其足百花釀雞好正
中菜(菜式很特別)有黑松露手撕雞、蝦多士(好過很多地方),魚米之鄉很特別,還有鮑魚兩食…值得一試,而且午餐還有真正有菠蘿的菠蘿包

It was our last full day in Hong Kong and I really wanted to try their dim sum.  My friends suggested this place since their family often dined here.  After doing some shopping in Causeway Bay, we used Google maps to find this little gem.  The place looked neat and patrons were chatting with one another while eating. Each of us ordered our favorite dishes.  The meal was excellent and affordable and the wait staff were so helpful...some also spoke to us in English. They even offered free wifi. =)
服務態度良好，食物有水準。
價錢雖不算便宜，但也不算貴，餸菜味道水準對得起個收費，家中兩老試過也收貨👍。試過拔絲咕嚕肉，炭燒牛肋骨，太極素菜羹，脆皮百花雞 .. 😋
